{"tid":579477,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"藝員拜年不見男主人接待 樂易玲驚傳婚變","createTime":"2018-03-03T15:51:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-04T11:37:22.000Z","uid":156068,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"82fd105c6c800a5076868414fd96906d28e1dd78","tid":579477,"uid":156068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-03T15:51:27.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】無線高層樂易玲被爆與結婚25年的建築師老公陳君毅婚姻破裂，有報道指陳君毅已搬離家，故今年大年初三，一眾藝人去樂易玲家拜年，已不見男主人幫手招呼賓客，當時樂易玲只謂老公外遊公幹，但就話有跟她較親近的藝人和同事，都知她的婚姻有問題。<br />\n<br />\n報道指有傳陳君毅另結新歡，加上他不滿老婆工作太忙乏略家庭，去年6月夫妻倆已討論這問題，樂易玲經過半年努力挽救婚姻仍然不果，她和兩個兒子情緒均大受困擾；其中細仔Ryan更被發現去年10月於instagram留言，透露了爸爸令家庭破裂，雖然絕望但仍存有希望。報道指跟陳君毅和樂易玲求證時，二人均矢口否認離婚傳聞，樂易玲更謂無論家庭和工作，她都盡全力不易放棄。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/03/235111_c3f3244c08b1ca02757ed98932c2b4ea.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F03%2F235111_c3f3244c08b1ca02757ed98932c2b4ea.jpg&h=d01237ce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"17ea741491307095157e6ffdd070afc1aa61fc39","tid":579477,"uid":156068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T09:23:54.000Z","msg":"離婚?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4da43c0c0375ae7a267a5b6c218f17a31bf5b68","tid":579477,"uid":156068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T11:37:22.000Z","msg":"樂易玲絕不放棄婚姻<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20180304/20321489\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180304%2F20321489&d=%2Fr0XaXq8KzlqI8IwtRVkZ8P%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=366def4e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180304%2F20321489&h=5dcec9ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainm